[genericglass Cocktail] Serving Glass: Cocktail Chilled

In Mixing Glass With Ice Add:
1 1/2 oz [genericingredient Brandy] Don Pedro Brandy
1/2 oz [genericingredient Apple Brandy] Lairds Apple Jack
1 tsp [genericingredient Lemon Juice] Lemon Juice
Dash Grenadine
Dash White Cr De Menthe
Shake and Strain

